37230>>>>>>>Class cPasswordHasher is a cObject
37231>>>>>>>    
37231>>>>>>>    Import_Class_Protocol cPasswordHasher_Mixin
37232>>>>>>>    
37232>>>>>>>    Procedure Construct_Object
37234>>>>>>>        Forward Send Construct_Object
37236>>>>>>>        
37236>>>>>>>        Property UInteger   peAlgorithm         C_PWH_PBKDF2_HMAC_SHA_512 
37237>>>>>>>        Property UInteger   puiSaltSize         16
37238>>>>>>>        
37238>>>>>>>        Property UInteger   puiOptTimeCost      420000
37239>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
37240>>>>>>>    
37240>>>>>>>    Function CreatePasswordHash String sPassword String ByRef sHash Returns Boolean
37242>>>>>>>        Boolean bOk
37242>>>>>>>        UInteger uiAlgo
37242>>>>>>>        Get peAlgorithm to uiAlgo
37243>>>>>>>        
37243>>>>>>>        Case Begin
37243>>>>>>>            Case (uiAlgo = C_PWH_PBKDF2_HMAC_SHA_256)
37245>>>>>>>            Case (uiAlgo = C_PWH_PBKDF2_HMAC_SHA_512)
37248>>>>>>>                Get CreatePasswordHashEx uiAlgo (puiSaltSize(Self)) sPassword (&sHash) (puiOptTimeCost(Self)) to bOk
37249>>>>>>>                Case Break
37250>>>>>>>            Case Else
37250>>>>>>>                Error 8710 "Invalid algorithm selected."
37251>>>>>>>>
37251>>>>>>>                Function_Return False
37252>>>>>>>        Case End
37252>>>>>>>        
37252>>>>>>>        Function_Return bOk
37253>>>>>>>    End_Function
37254>>>>>>>    
37254>>>>>>>    Function RequiredBufferSize Returns UBigInt
37256>>>>>>>        UBigInt ullSize
37256>>>>>>>        UInteger uiAlgo
37256>>>>>>>        Get peAlgorithm to uiAlgo
37257>>>>>>>        
37257>>>>>>>        Case Begin
37257>>>>>>>            Case (uiAlgo = C_PWH_PBKDF2_HMAC_SHA_256)
37259>>>>>>>            Case (uiAlgo = C_PWH_PBKDF2_HMAC_SHA_512)
37262>>>>>>>                Get RequiredBufferSizeEx uiAlgo (puiSaltSize(Self)) (puiOptTimeCost(Self)) to ullSize
37263>>>>>>>                Case Break
37264>>>>>>>            Case Else
37264>>>>>>>                Error 8710 "Invalid algorithm selected."
37265>>>>>>>>
37265>>>>>>>                Function_Return 0
37266>>>>>>>        Case End
37266>>>>>>>        
37266>>>>>>>        Function_Return ullSize
37267>>>>>>>    End_Function
37268>>>>>>>
37268>>>>>>>End_Class
